GitHub/LED-matrixes-controller-programmer
https://github.com/Bntdumas/LED-matrixes-controller-programmer
----------------------------------------------

The computer part is able to simulate a led matrix (in 2 or 3 dimensions) and create some led scenarios. It can communicate with an arduino.

The arduino (+ schematics) part is the hardware used for my early tests.

More explanations to come.


Arduino project needs library cmdMessenger:
http://arduino.cc/playground/Code/CmdMessenger

LibCommArduino Qt library need QExtSerialPort library:
http://code.google.com/p/qextserialport/

